data.title: Kelly Johnson - Packaging Engineer at PopSockets
data.meta_description: Kelly Johnson has a diverse work experience in the field of packaging engineering.
data.text:
Kelly Johnson has a diverse work experience in the field of packaging engineering. Kelly started their career as a Packaging Engineer Intern at ACCO Brands in 2015. Kelly then worked at Pernod Ricard as a Package Development Specialist from 2017 to 2018. Following that, they joined Libbey Inc. as a Packaging Engineer from 2018 to 2020. Currently, they are working at PopSockets, where they have held multiple roles including Packaging Coordinator, Associate Packaging Engineer, and currently as a Packaging Engineer.

Kelly Johnson attended Michigan State University from 2013 to 2016, where they obtained a Bachelor of Science degree in Packaging.
